        public static ChartPanel createGraphPanel(java.lang.String title,
                                          java.lang.String axisX,
                                          java.lang.String axisY,
                                          XYSeriesCollection data,
                                          int orientation,
                                          boolean legend,
                                          boolean tooltip,
                                          boolean url,
                                          int mode,
                                          boolean showShape,
                                          boolean showLine,
                                          boolean fillShape,
                                          java.awt.Color bgColor)
        Return the graphic panel that should be added on the JFrame
        Parameters:
        title - The title of the Graph
        axisX - The title of the X axis
        axisY - The title of the Y axis
        data - A XYSeriesCollection containing the data to be plotted
        showLine - Show line between points
        showShape - Show shapes on points
        shapeFill - Fill shapes
        autoSort - Sort data automatically by X values
        allowDuplicateXValues - Allow/Disallow duplicated X values
        backcolor - The default background color of the graph
        orientation - The default orientation of the graph (0-HORIZONTAL;1-VERTICAL)
        showLegend - Show legend
        createTooltip - Create tooltip
        createURL - Create URL
        modeGraph - (0-exact;1-Rounded Curve;2-Area)
        Returns:
        CharPanel component with the specified proprierties
